summary: This document contains a certification of business records from Lauren Kwintner, a legal assistant at JENE Inc., regarding the maintenance of business records related to the company. It includes an appendix listing various documents produced in response to a subpoena, including IRS forms and aircraft registration details. This document contains various financial records and tax notices related to entities and individuals, including delinquent tax notices and annual franchise tax reports. It highlights the financial obligations of certain entities in Delaware and New York, as well as the associated penalties for non-compliance.
